Acceptance: Provider exposure, search, and invocation enforce the frozen mcp_servers policy. Invocation uses the in-flight access snapshot; HTTP credentials are leased per call and credential-bearing stdio clients are scope-keyed or rejected. Two differently granted Rooms cannot see or use each others servers or credentials. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.